    <entry>
      <title>Why &quot; Try to  be  not perfect &quot;？</title>
      <link href="/2026/03/17/Try%20%20to%20be%20not%20perfect/"/>
      <url>/2026/03/17/Try%20%20to%20be%20not%20perfect/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>灵感来源于B站看到的一个TED演讲视频</p><p><a href="https://www.bilibili.com/video/av116050133849523/" title="为什么聪明人在二十多岁时会失败">为什么聪明人在二十多岁时会失败</a></p><div style="position: relative; width: 100%; height: 0; padding-bottom: 56.25%; margin: 20px 0; border-radius: 12px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); background: #000;">  <iframe src="https://player.bilibili.com/player.html?aid=116050133849523&page=1&as_wide=1&high_quality=1&danmaku=0&t=0"           style="position: absolute; width: 100%; height: 100%; left: 0; top: 0;"           scrolling="no" border="0" frameborder="no" framespacing="0" allowfullscreen="true"          sandbox="allow-top-navigation allow-same-origin allow-forms allow-scripts">  </iframe></div><div class="motto-container" style="    background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8), rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8)), url('https://fastly.jsdelivr.net/gh/KingPenguinMan/image-bed/img/astronaut-black-hole-deep-space-universe-cosmos-surreal-3840x2160-6743.jpg');    background-size: cover;    background-position: center;    background-attachment: fixed;    padding: 60px 20px;    border-radius: 15px;    margin: 40px auto;    max-width: 900px;    box-shadow: 0 15px 35px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);    color: #f0f0f0;    font-family: 'PingFang SC', 'Microsoft YaHei', sans-serif;    line-height: 2;">  <p style="font-size: 1.6rem; font-weight: 300; border-left: 5px solid #fb7299; padding-left: 25px; margin-bottom: 50px; text-shadow: 0 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);">    道理显而易见：<br>    <span style="color: #fb7299; font-weight: bold;">努力</span>会打破“天才”的滤镜。<br>    如果不努力，失败都能归结于：<span style="text-decoration: underline; text-decoration-color: #fb7299;">“我没认真。”</span>  </p>  <p style="font-size: 1.2rem; margin-bottom: 30px; opacity: 0.95;">    总是筹划着学点什么，还没开始，路线、建议、避坑指南便已看得数不胜数。<br>    盯着那几十小时的学习时长，最终望而止步。  </p>  <p style="font-size: 1.2rem; margin-bottom: 30px; opacity: 0.95;">    总想系统地学习，枯燥的底层知识却又难以下咽。  </p>  <div style="background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03); padding: 30px; border-radius: 12px; margin: 50px 0; border: 1px dashed rgba(255,255,255,0.15); backdrop-filter: blur(5px);">    <p style="font-size: 1.4rem; margin: 0; text-align: center; letter-spacing: 3px; font-weight: 500;">      永远不要忘记，曾经的成功是用<span style="color: #fb7299;">努力</span>换来的。    </p>  </div>  <p style="font-size: 1.2rem; margin-bottom: 40px; opacity: 0.95;">    如果能成功，怎么努力都不为过。<br>    毕竟在他人看来，<span style="background: linear-gradient(to right, transparent, rgba(251,114,153,0.2), transparent); padding: 2px 5px;">结果远大于过程</span>。  </p>  <p style="font-size: 2.2rem; font-weight: 900; text-align: center; margin-top: 60px; color: #fb7299; text-shadow: 0 0 25px rgba(251,114,153,0.5); letter-spacing: 1px;">    So, try to be NOT perfect.  </p></div><div style="padding: 20px; border-left: 5px solid #fb7299; background: rgba(251, 114, 153, 0.1); border-radius: 8px; margin: 20px 0;">  <p style="font-size: 1.25rem; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 10px; color: #efefef;">    前进，前进，不择手段地前进！  </p>  <p style="text-align: right; font-size: 1rem; color: #888; margin: 0;">    —— 维德 《三体》  </p></div>]]></content>
      
      
      
